{"id":153,"parent_id":141,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":153,"title":"1 Corinthians 12","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Cor.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 12"],[".studySummary",["i","The Holy Ghost reveals that Jesus is the Christ—Spiritual gifts are present among the Saints—Apostles, prophets, and miracles are found in the true Church."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.1","order":"03.09.012.17800"},["b","1"],"Now concerning spiritual",["i","gifts,"],"brethren, I would not have you ignorant."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.2","order":"03.09.012.17801"},["b","2"],"Ye know that ye were Gentiles,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"carried away"],"unto these dumb",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"idols"],", even as ye were led."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.3","order":"03.09.012.17802"},["b","3"],"Wherefore I give you to understand, that no man speaking by the Spirit of God calleth Jesus accursed: and",["i","that"],"no man can",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"say"],"that Jesus is the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"Lord"],", but by the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"Holy Ghost"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.4","order":"03.09.012.17803"},["b","4"],"Now there are diversities of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"gifts"],", but the same Spirit."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.5","order":"03.09.012.17804"},["b","5"],"And there are differences of administrations, but the same Lord."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.6","order":"03.09.012.17805"},["b","6"],"And there are diversities of operations, but it is the same God which worketh all in all."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.7","order":"03.09.012.17806"},["b","7"],"But the manifestation of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Spirit"],"is given to every man to profit withal."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.8","order":"03.09.012.17807"},["b","8"],"For to one is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"given"],"by the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"Spirit"],"the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"word"],"of",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_8d"},"wisdom"],"; to another the word of",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_8e"},"knowledge"],"by the same Spirit;"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.9","order":"03.09.012.17808"},["b","9"],"To another",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"faith"],"by the same Spirit; to another the gifts of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"healing"],"by the same Spirit;"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.10","order":"03.09.012.17809"},["b","10"],"To another the working of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"miracles"],"; to another",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"prophecy"],"; to another",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"discerning"],"of spirits; to another",["i","divers"],"kinds of tongues; to another the interpretation of",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"tongues"],":"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.11","order":"03.09.012.17810"},["b","11"],"But all these worketh that one and the selfsame Spirit, dividing to every man severally as he will."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.12","order":"03.09.012.17811"},["b","12"],"For as the body is one, and hath many members, and all the members of that one body, being many, are one body: so also",["i","is"],"Christ."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.13","order":"03.09.012.17812"},["b","13"],"For by one Spirit are we all baptized into one",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"body"],", whether",["i","we be"],"Jews or",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"Gentiles"],", whether",["i","we be"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"bond"],"or free; and have been all made to drink into one Spirit."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.14","order":"03.09.012.17813"},["b","14"],"For the body is not one member, but many."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.15","order":"03.09.012.17814"},["b","15"],"If the foot shall say, Because I am not the hand, I am not of the body; is it therefore not of the body?"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.16","order":"03.09.012.17815"},["b","16"],"And if the ear shall say, Because I am not the eye, I am not of the body; is it therefore not of the body?"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.17","order":"03.09.012.17816"},["b","17"],"If the whole body",["i","were"],"an eye, where",["i","were"],"the hearing? If the whole",["i","were"],"hearing, where",["i","were"],"the smelling?"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.18","order":"03.09.012.17817"},["b","18"],"But now hath God set the members every one of them in the body, as it hath pleased him."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.19","order":"03.09.012.17818"},["b","19"],"And if they were all one member, where",["i","were"],"the body?"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.20","order":"03.09.012.17819"},["b","20"],"But now",["i","are they"],"many members, yet but one body."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.21","order":"03.09.012.17820"},["b","21"],"And the eye cannot say unto the hand, I have no need of thee: nor again the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"head"],"to the feet, I have no need of you."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.22","order":"03.09.012.17821"},["b","22"],"Nay, much more those members of the body, which seem to be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"more feeble"],", are necessary:"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.23","order":"03.09.012.17822"},["b","23"],"And those",["i","members"],"of the body, which we think to be less honourable, upon these we bestow more abundant honour; and our uncomely",["i","parts"],"have more abundant comeliness."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.24","order":"03.09.012.17823"},["b","24"],"For our comely",["i","parts"],"have no need: but God hath tempered the body together, having given more abundant honour to that",["i","part"],"which lacked:"],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.25","order":"03.09.012.17824"},["b","25"],"That there should be no schism in the body; but",["i","that"],"the members should have the same",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"care"],"one for another."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.26","order":"03.09.012.17825"},["b","26"],"And whether one member",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"suffer"],", all the members",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"suffer"],"with it; or one member be honoured, all the members rejoice with it."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.27","order":"03.09.012.17826"},["b","27"],"Now ye are the body of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"Christ"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"members"],"in particular."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.28","order":"03.09.012.17827"},["b","28"],"And God hath set some in the church, first",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"apostles"],", secondarily",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"prophets"],", thirdly",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_28c"},"teachers"],", after that miracles, then gifts of healings, helps,",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_28d"},"governments"],", diversities of tongues."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.29","order":"03.09.012.17828"},["b","29"],["i","Are"],"all apostles?",["i","are"],"all prophets?",["i","are"],"all teachers?",["i","are"],"all workers of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"miracles"],"?"],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.30","order":"03.09.012.17829"},["b","30"],"Have all the gifts of healing? do all speak with tongues? do all interpret?"],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.31","order":"03.09.012.17830"},["b","31"],"But",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"covet earnestly"],"the best",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_31b"},"gifts"],": and yet shew I unto you a more",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_31c"},"excellent"],"way."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.2a","order":"03.09.012.17831"},["b","2a"],["span.small","GR"],"led astray."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.2b","order":"03.09.012.17833"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/idolatry"},"TG Idolatry"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.3a","order":"03.09.012.17835"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/revelation"},"TG Revelation"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/testimony"},"Testimony"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.3b","order":"03.09.012.17837"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-lord"},"TG Jesus Christ, Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.3c","order":"03.09.012.17839"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/6.44.44,63-65"},"John 6:44 (44, 63–65)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-mission-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Mission of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-source-of-testimony"},"Holy Ghost, Source of Testimony"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/inspiration"},"Inspiration"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.4a","order":"03.09.012.17841"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-gifts-of"},"TG God, Gifts of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-gifts-of"},"Holy Ghost, Gifts of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-mission-of"},"Holy Ghost, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.7a","order":"03.09.012.17843"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.16.8-18"},"D&C 46:16 (8–18)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-spirit-of"},"TG God, Spirit of"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.8a","order":"03.09.012.17845"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.23"},"D&C 35:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.8b","order":"03.09.012.17847"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.7"},"D&C 25:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.19"},"35:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.8c","order":"03.09.012.17849"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/89.2"},"D&C 89:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"8d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.8d","order":"03.09.012.17851"},["b","8d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wisdom"},"TG Wisdom"],"."],["div",{"id":"8e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.8e","order":"03.09.012.17853"},["b","8e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/10.10"},"Moro. 10:10"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-gifts-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Gifts of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/knowledge"},"Knowledge"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.9a","order":"03.09.012.17855"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/faith"},"TG Faith"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.9b","order":"03.09.012.17857"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/heal"},"TG Heal"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.10a","order":"03.09.012.17859"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/miracle"},"TG Miracle"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.10b","order":"03.09.012.17861"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophecy"},"TG Prophecy"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.10c","order":"03.09.012.17863"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/discernment-spiritual"},"TG Discernment, Spiritual"],"."],["div",{"id":"10d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.10d","order":"03.09.012.17865"},["b","10d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/language"},"TG Language"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.13a","order":"03.09.012.17867"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/church"},"TG Church"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.13b","order":"03.09.012.17869"},["b","13b"],["span.small","GR"],"Greeks.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/3.11"},"Col. 3:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.13c","order":"03.09.012.17871"},["b","13c"],["span.small","GR"],"slaves.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/24.11"},"D&C 24:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.20"},"43:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.21a","order":"03.09.012.17873"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.109"},"D&C 84:109"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/leadership"},"TG Leadership"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.22a","order":"03.09.012.17875"},["b","22a"],["span.small","GR"],"weaker."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.25a","order":"03.09.012.17877"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/1.10.10-15"},"1 Cor. 1:10 (10–15)"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.26a","order":"03.09.012.17879"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/suffering"},"TG Suffering"],"."],["div",{"id":"26b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.26b","order":"03.09.012.17881"},["b","26b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/compassion"},"TG Compassion"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.27a","order":"03.09.012.17883"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-head-of-the-church"},"TG Jesus Christ, Head of the Church"],"."],["div",{"id":"27b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.27b","order":"03.09.012.17885"},["b","27b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/church-organization"},"TG Church Organization"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.28a","order":"03.09.012.17887"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostles"},"TG Apostles"],"."],["div",{"id":"28b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.28b","order":"03.09.012.17889"},["b","28b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophets-mission-of"},"TG Prophets, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"28c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.28c","order":"03.09.012.17891"},["b","28c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/teacher"},"TG Teacher"],"."],["div",{"id":"28d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.28d","order":"03.09.012.17893"},["b","28d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/governments"},"TG Governments"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.29a","order":"03.09.012.17895"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/miracle"},"TG Miracle"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.31a","order":"03.09.012.17897"},["b","31a"],["span.small","GR"],"seek earnestly, be zealous for.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.8.8-9"},"D&C 46:8 (8–9)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/covet"},"TG Covet"],"."],["div",{"id":"31b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.31b","order":"03.09.012.17899"},["b","31b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-gifts-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Gifts of"],"."],["div",{"id":"31c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/12.31c","order":"03.09.012.17901"},["b","31c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/12.11.11-12,32"},"Ether 12:11 (11–12, 32)"],"."]]}
